= render 'sidebar_content'
.container.jumbotron
  = image_tag('tw-small0.png', class: 'image')
  %h1 Climbing Judge
  %p Climbing Judge is the app that helps judge climbing competitions.
  %p For now it covers only one of three climbing disciplines - LEAD (Lead, Bouldering, Speed).
  %p
    To use it, please #{link_to "signup", signup_path} with your real email address and
    follow the instructions.
  %h2 LEAD
  %p Lead competition consists of three rounds: eliminations, semi-finals and finals.
  %p
    In eliminations every competitor climbs on each of two eliminations routes.
    The result of this round is calculated by combining scores from both routes.
  %p
    Twenty six best from eliminations start in semi-finals.
    Semi-Finals are optional in case there is a small number of competitors.
  %p Eight best from semi-finals start in finals.
